title: This Game Surprised Me! I Built the SPOOKIEST Castle in Tiny Glade.
description:
Hello Everyone! Today we're hopping into the new Cozy Building Game Tiny Glade! I must say I was pleasantly surprised with how much I enjoy building in this game. October means its time for a spooky project, I hope you enjoy this dark castle/town! Happy Spooky Season everyone! Hope you enjoy!

Thank you to my lovely Patrons! link down below if you'd like to support the content!
Link: https://www.patreon.com/SmittySurvival
